gov bob martinez the session ended with the resounding defeat of 
martinezs legislation as thousands protested outside the capitol 
the disappointing loss led antiabortion forces to train their 
guns on shaw the only one of the justices to face a retention 
election this year 
under florida law supreme court justices are initially 
